;;; Commentary:

;; Low distraction, minimalistic color theme, with minimal colors, preferring
;; other styles of markup (italic, bold).

;;; Credits:

;; Based on:
;; http://github.com/maio/eink-emacs

;; Which in turn was inspired by:
;;
;; https://bitbucket.org/kisom/eink.vim
